  <titles>
    <title as="introduced" type="short">No Taxation Without Representation Act of 2001</title>
    <title as="introduced" type="official">To provide for full voting representation in the Congress for the citizens of the District of Columbia, to amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to provide that individuals who are residents of the District of Columbia shall be exempt from Federal income taxation until such full voting representation takes effect, and for other purposes.</title>
